Package version2.prototype.summary.temporal

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    InterpolateStrategy
    Interface designed for defining interpolation strategies for temporal summary calculations.
    MergeStrategy
    Merging strategy template to be used in temporal summary for creating classes to define how to create composite data files.
    TemporalSummaryCompositionStrategy
    Interface designed for defining temporal summary composition strategies (methods by which to combine the raster files to create temporal composites).
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AvgGdalRasterFileMerge
    Concrete MergeStrategy.
    CDCWeeklyStrategy
    An implementation of TemporalSummaryCompositionStrategy representing a strategy for creating weekly composites based on the CDC calendar.
    FileDatePair
    Pairing object of a File object and a DataDate object.
    GregorianMonthlyStrategy
    An implementation of TemporalSummaryCompositionStrategy representing a strategy for creating monthly composites based on the Gregorian calendar.
    GregorianWeeklyStrategy
    An implementation of TemporalSummaryCompositionStrategy representing a strategy for creating weekly composites based on the Gregorian calendar.
    TemporalSummaryCalculator
    Calculates the temporal summary for given raster files using a shared stored list of files to create composites from.
    TemporalSummaryComposition
    Represents a temporal summary composition either partial or complete.
    TemporalSummaryRasterFileStore
    Storage object for temporal summary raster files.
    WHOWeeklyStrategy
    An implementation of TemporalSummaryCompositionStrategy representing a strategy for creating weekly composites based on the WHO calendar.
